{"tid":2093343,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港和芬蘭","createTime":"2020-07-03T18:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T18:40:06.000Z","uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66a26a2f4b2cb5fa6a658838ce527878c3891bde","tid":2093343,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:26:32.000Z","msg":"其實香港同芬蘭好似<br />\n<br />\n一開始都係帝國嘅邊緣。 垃圾地方<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭大公國得到亞歷山大一世許諾的自主性。<br />\n而香港就係新安不管，鄉紳橫行，港英粗管嘅埠區。<br />\n<br />\n後來都發展不錯，但是很尷尬地夾在中西之間。<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭人幸運得到德國嘅幫助，加入在德jager營進行軍事訓練。其後在冬季戰爭輸少當贏。<br />\n<br />\n香港人呢？"},{"pid":"786b47758bbc3c44ad897c2f037a9f3f95cf7eed","tid":2093343,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"冬季戰爭&ldquo;曼那海姆&rdquo;防線打到蘇聯傻仔咁，有興趣可以search <br />\nsausage night.<br />\n當時，<br />\n真正嘅冬將軍+高級軍事指揮家曼那海姆+國民積極性大敗大清洗後蘇軍。<br />\n24萬女國民加入防空民防團體<br />\nLotta svard<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKBnV0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKBnV0L.jpg&h=3e089816&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3e54ce651fd537f3d16a9bdbc81a0ae25ef5cc1","tid":2093343,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:40:06.000Z","msg":"其實對於我們的處境，我想這幾個國家會特別有體會：<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭（冬季戰爭）<br />\n捷克（布拉格之春，連儂牆，天鵝絨）<br />\n斯洛伐克。（同上，以前一個國家）<br />\n波羅的海三國（立陶宛，拉脫維亞，愛沙尼亞）（人鍊奇蹟）<br />\n<br />\n本應有德國（柏林牆）<br />\n但德法宜家似乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以色列應該WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該嘗試大家一齊做多國文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就做左喇<br />\n你呢？<br />\n<br />\n或許還有：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}